baseline_groups.claim_summary: Ethnic minority hosts on Airbnb charge lower prices (ethnic price gap), measured by minodummy coefficient in log_price regression with city-wave and/or neighborhood fixed effects.
baseline_groups.notes: Table 2 columns 1-4. Col4 with block+city-wave FE + controls is preferred. All measure same estimand under different conditioning sets.

global_notes: 77 valid specifications with no missing/invalid data. Main claim: ethnic minority hosts receive lower Airbnb prices. Heterogeneity specs report main effect of minodummy from interaction models (reference group effect). robust/control/none is numerically identical to baseline_table2_col1.
